      "versionNonce": 1,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Runs: run_worker_loop_forever()\nListens on tcp://:26600\n\n8x TrainingActor (one per GPU)\n  → FaultTolerantTrainer.train()\n  → FSDP AllReduce via NCCL\n\n8x FailureActor (one per GPU)\n  → SEGFAULT / KILL_PROC / COMMS\n\nTorchFT Manager (rank 0 = server)\n  → heartbeats + quorum to Lighthouse",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Runs: run_worker_loop_forever()\nListens on tcp://:26600\n\n8x TrainingActor (one per GPU)\n  → FaultTolerantTrainer.train()\n  → FSDP AllReduce via NCCL\n\n8x FailureActor (one per GPU)\n  → SEGFAULT / KILL_PROC / COMMS\n\nTorchFT Manager (rank 0 = server)\n  → heartbeats + quorum to Lighthouse",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
