    },
    {
      "id": "supervision-tree",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 50,
      "y": 1175,
      "width": 700,
      "height": 250,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 49,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 1,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Root Actor (controller main process)\n│\n├── ReplicaActor 0  ← holds HostMesh 0, __supervise__ catches faults\n│   ├── TrainingActor 0..7  (remote, GPU pod 0)\n│   └── FailureActor 0..7   (remote, GPU pod 0)\n│\n└── ReplicaActor 1  ← holds HostMesh 1, __supervise__ catches faults\n    ├── TrainingActor 0..7  (remote, GPU pod 1)\n    └── FailureActor 0..7   (remote, GPU pod 1)\n\nProcess dies → __supervise__ returns True → fault stops at ReplicaActor\n→ inner retry: host_mesh.spawn_procs() again (same pod, fast)\n→ outer retry (if pod dies): recreate K8s job (slow, fallback only)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "flow-title",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 50,
      "y": 1460,
      "width": 400,
      "height": 30,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 50,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 1,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "LIFECYCLE FLOW",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LIFECYCLE FLOW",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "flow-text",
