      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Red     = K8s (control plane, API, Operator)\nBlue    = Our code (controller pod, Monarch actors)\nGreen   = TorchFT (Lighthouse, quorum, recovery)\nOrange  = ReplicaActor (supervision boundary)\nPurple  = GPU Pods (training workers)\n\nController = our orchestration code (we wrote it)\nOperator   = Monarch K8s component (pre-installed)",
